00154         public static
00155         ComplexVector
00156         Create(
00157             IList<double> realComponents,
00158             IList<double> imagComponents
00159             )
00160         {
00161             if(null == realComponents)
00162             {
00163                 throw new ArgumentNullException("realComponents");
00164             }
00165 
00166             if(null == imagComponents)
00167             {
00168                 throw new ArgumentNullException("imagComponents");
00169             }
00170 
00171             if(realComponents.Count != imagComponents.Count)
00172             {
00173                 throw new ArgumentException(Properties.Resources.ArgumentVectorsSameLengths);
00174             }
00175 
00176             Complex[] newData = new Complex[realComponents.Count];
00177             for(int i = 0; i < newData.Length; i++)
00178             {
00179                 newData[i] = new Complex(realComponents[i], imagComponents[i]);
00180             }
00181 
00182             return new ComplexVector(newData);
00183         }

00875         public static
00876         ComplexVector
00877         CrossProduct(
00878             IVector<Complex> u,
00879             IVector<Complex> v
00880             )
00881         {
00882             CheckMatchingVectorDimensions(u, v);
00883             if(3 != u.Length)
00884             {
00885                 throw new ArgumentOutOfRangeException("u", Resources.ArgumentVectorThreeDimensional);
00886             }
00887 
00888             ComplexVector product = new ComplexVector(new Complex[] {
00889                 u[1]*v[2] - u[2]*v[1],
00890                 u[2]*v[0] - u[0]*v[2],
00891                 u[0]*v[1] - u[1]*v[0]
00892                 });
00893 
00894             return product;
00895         }
